package: LayerSelect mode
author: Autodesk, Inc.
organization: Autodesk, Inc.
version: 1.7
requires: 
rv: 4.0.7
openrv: 1.0.0
optional: true

modes: 
  - file: layer_select_mode.mu
    menu: Tools/Layer Selector
    shortcut: '/' 
    event: 'key-down--/'
    load: delay

description: |

  <p>
  This unsupported Package implements a Layer Select Widget to make it easy to
  choose which layer to view from multi-layer exr files.
  </p>

  <p>
  Open the Layer Selector widget with the '/' hot key. Select desired layer by
  clicking. Or, scroll the mouse wheel to move the selection target to the
  desired layer. Then select with a click of the mouse wheel to set the
  selected layer.
  </p>

  <p>
  This widget can be docked in the margin or allowed to float. Right click for
  the settings menu to change the setting.
  <p>

